        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/24695",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Have you set a cache for your translations ?\nHave you tried this several times ?\n\nI expect that your 8 seconds come from loading the translation data in memory from disk.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-09-28T23:46:41.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-09-28T23:46:41.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/24699",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=duckwilliamson",
                        "name": "duckwilliamson",
                        "displayName": "Duck Williamson",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I have not set a cache (do I need to?), but instead attempted to disable translations with $form->setDisableTranslator(true); (I don't intend to have any translation on the site at all)\nThe 8 seconds was on an old dev computer I was using, my current new computer after several attempts has an average load time (for just the form load - not the whole page) of 2.52 seconds. With the two functions edited to just return* the average time is 0.38 seconds.\n\n*The overridden functions are as follows:\nprotected function _translateOption($option, $value)\n{\n   if (!isset($this->_translated[$option])) {\n      $this->options[$option] = $value;\n      $this->_translated[$option] = true;\n      return true;\n   }\n   return false;\n}\n\nprotected function _translateValue($value)\n{\n   return $value;\n}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=duckwilliamson",
                        "name": "duckwilliamson",
                        "displayName": "Duck Williamson",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-09-29T01:21:47.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-09-29T01:21:47.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/25530",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "A patch has been applied to trunk to bail early from _translateOption() if the disableTranslator flag is true. Another user has verified that this speeds operations at the same factor as reported with commenting out the call.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
